        "content_kRdryg": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why Medicinal Mad Honey?",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>Driven by a deep respect for community values and for nature and people, we take absolute care for the journey of our mad honey from <a href=\"/pages/hive-to-jar\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hive to jar\">Himalayan hive to jar</a>. For eight years, we’ve closely collaborated with over 80 communities and more than 2,100 <a href=\"/pages/honey-hunter\" title=\"Honey Hunters\">honey hunters</a> across Lamjung, Gorkha, Jarjarkot, Rukum, Solukhumbu, Rolpa, Darchula, and Dolakha in Nepal. Our harvesting process only occurs twice a year, delivering unmatched potency and purity in every jar.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
